      <title>认识BLE5协议栈[二]--安全管理层</title>
      <link>https://MHz-Xing.github.io/blog/2019-12/%E8%AE%A4%E8%AF%86ble5%E5%8D%8F%E8%AE%AE%E6%A0%88%E4%BA%8C-%E5%AE%89%E5%85%A8%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%B1%82/</link>
